Warhead: Inferno and Rage, get me the shape of that thing.

He then began to think on the two other reports, those of Nightshade 
and Drillbit. He had never seen an energon mass of variable stability, 
and the fact that it was 20 meters deep implied either two things. 
Either the movement of the planet had brought it this close to the 
surface, or it had been placed there purposefully. This was a strange 
thing to deal with. However, he was still willing to take the sample 
himself.
